description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an experienced Clinical Psychologist to join the Early Intervention Team within the Specialist Services Division of Pennine Care NHS Foundation Trust on a fixed term contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post-holder will be based within the Early Intervention Team within Bury, an integrated multi-professional health and social care team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post offers the opportunity to provide highly specialised clinical psychology services to adults and young people experiencing severe and enduring mental illness who have highly complex psychological needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will involve delivering multi-dimensional psychological assessments, risk assessments, formulations and a range of psychological interventions and therapy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Nicola Innes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Team Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: n.innes1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 0161 253 7441&lt;/p&gt;
